name: Metamorphosis 2.0
description:
She came to me, a dancing ballerina with such calm and kindness. I saw the thorns cutting into her flesh like knives, but her face didn't show pain -it showed joy. Blood gushing as she danced, and danced, and danced. One ballerina pirouette after the other, until there she was, not a shackled woman dancing through her pain, but a Butterfly who turned her pain into wings.

Read the story behind the art: https://www.alteredgenie.com/post/metamorphosis-2-0
